</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Will Smith FB、IG 發文道歉，大批網民留言：支持及諒解保護家人的行為</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/29/weunderstandsmith/hottopic/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=weunderstandsmith</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[samuel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 29 Mar 2022 04:26:24 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活娛樂]]></category><category><![CDATA[社交網絡]]></category><category><![CDATA[will smith]]></category><category><![CDATA[奧斯卡 2022]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1093011</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>今日（3 月 29 號），奧斯卡新科影帝韋史密夫（Will Smith）在 Instagram 及 Faceb [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">今日（3 月 29 號），奧斯卡新科影帝韋史密夫（Will Smith）在 Instagram 及 Facebook 上發文，就昨日（3 月 28 號）在奧斯卡頒獎典禮上怒摑基斯洛克一事致歉。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1093019" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-29-上午 11.56.58-694x369.png" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-29-上午 11.56.58-694x369.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-29-上午 11.56.58-1280x680.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-29-上午 11.56.58-768x408.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-29-上午 11.56.58.png 1282w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWillSmith%2Fposts%2F544176300403935&amp;show_text=true&amp;width=500" width="500" height="742" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">韋史密夫指所有暴力行為都是有害的，而自己昨日的失態舉動不可接受，亦沒有藉口。他明白從事娛樂圈事業難免被開玩笑，但當事件觸及到自己妻子的病況，則無法忍受，所以導致情緒化舉動。</span></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-